58
00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:40.680
This method is really, really super useful

59
00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:42.960
We call it the human color hint

60
00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:46.240
You can directly specify that AI plays a certain expert

61
00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:47.600
For example, you tell him

62
00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:50.760
