89
00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:48.560
I'll learn it right away

90
00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:49.680
The fourth skill

91
00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:53.600
It is important to clearly specify the limit of output

92
00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:55.360
For example, you can't just tell him

93
00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:56.640
Help me design a website

94
00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:57.960
It's too blurry

95
00:03:57.960 --> 00:03:59.960
You have to give him specific conditions like this

96
00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:02.520
For example, the guide list must be fixed on top

97
00:04:02.520 --> 00:04:04.440
The color should be the kind of sunset color

98
00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:07.400
And there should be a dark and light color mode to switch

99
00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:09.480
The clearer the frame you give

100
00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:10.680
What he does

101
00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:13.080
The more it will be the way you want

102
00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:14.720
Okay, the fifth skill

103
00:04:14.720 --> 00:04:18.320
Solve the complex tasks one by one

104
00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:19.800
This method is also very famous

105
00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:22.440
It's called a thought chain hint

106
00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:24.680
Don't just throw a big question to him

107
00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:27.240
Like helping me analyze the sales data of this season

108
00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:29.200
