110
00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:34.880
The first step is to find the best product

111
00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:36.920
The second step is to compare with the previous season

112
00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:39.640
The third step is to find out which trends are very special

113
00:04:39.640 --> 00:04:41.920
The fourth step is to try to guess the reason

114
00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:44.320
You see, when you take him step by step

115
00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:45.920
He can follow your logic

116
00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:48.440
